  <brief_title>Quad Resection (Hot Snare vs Cold Snare vs Hot EMR vs Cold EMR)</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Randomized Trial Comparing the Effectiveness of Polyp Resection Treatments (Hot Snare vs Cold Snare vs Hot EMR vs Cold EMR)</official_title>
